; Regression test for issue #859: %a used in format strings returns error (BZ#859)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/859
; %a in format strings should return the account name, not an error.

2024/01/01 Test Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%a\n'
Expenses:Food
Assets:Cash
end test
